2. DICOM upload

  Effort: Low-Medium. Payoff: High.

  Without this you can only demo your own hardcoded data. Any 
  audience will immediately want to drag their own scan in. On
   the backend it's a POST /api/upload that saves the file and
   re-runs manager.load(). On the frontend it's a
  drag-and-drop zone. ~100 lines total. This is table stakes  
  for a demo — you need it before Docker.